high_descs: Walk towards the toaster, turn right, walk towards the sink.
Open the cabinet above the sink, then take the cup out, close the door.
Turn all the way around, then walk towards the refrigerator.
Place the cup on the top shelf of the refrigerator next to a tomato, then close the door.
Remove the cup from the refrigerator, then turn left towards the coffee maker.
Place the cup in the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Place a cup in the coffee maker.

high_descs: Walk straight to the kitchen counter
Open the top cabinet door to get a coffee cup
Carry the coffee cup over to the fridge
Open the door to the fridge and put the cup inside for a few seconds, then open the door and take the cup out
Carry the chilled coffee cup over to the coffee pot
Put the coffee cup on the coffee maker
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled coffee cup on the coffee maker

high_descs: Walk two steps forward then turn right and walk to the counter that's to the left of the sink and stand squarely in front of it.
Open the cupboard in front of you and get the mug you see there.
Take a step back and then turn right and walk over to the fridge that's on your left.
Chill the mug in the fridge then get it back out and close the door.
Take a step to your left and walk to the coffee maker in front of you so you can use it.
Put the mug under the coffee maker's spout.
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled mug under the coffee maker.
